  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "India denies the news about sending the Indian army to Sri Lanka!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Indian High Commission in Sri Lanka has categorically denied the media and social media speculations about India sending its army to Sri Lanka.",
        "The High Commission would like to categorically refute the media and social media speculations about India sending its army to Sri Lanka. Government of India does not agree with these statements and such comments.",
        "A spokesperson for the Indian Ministry of External Affairs has already made it clear that India stands with the people of Sri Lanka as they seek to realize their aspirations for prosperity and progress through democratic means and values, institutions and constitutional framework established accordingly, the tweet said.",
        "Meanwhile, the BJP has said that it is ready to send the Indian Army to support Mahinda Rajapaksa and President Kotaya if they request them. Subramanian Swamy, the senior leader of , had shared a comment on his official Twitter page.",
        "It said, \u201cBoth Gotabaya and Mahinda Rajapaksa were elected with absolute majority in free elections. How can India allow a gang to subvert such a legitimate election?",
        "Then no democratic country in our neighborhood will be safe. We are ready to provide India's military assistance when the Rajapaksas demand it,\" Subramanian Swamy said on his Twitter page.",
        "Thus the Indian BJP It is noteworthy that the comment made by the senior leader of Subramanian Swamy on his official Twitter page appeared in the media and social media."
      ],
